    <tr><td>Format / Beautify</td><td><a href="/tools/json-formatter/">JSON Formatter</a></td><td>Reading minified API responses or configs</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Minify JSON</td><td><a href="/tools/json-formatter/">JSON Formatter</a></td><td>Reducing payload size for production</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Convert JSON to YAML</td><td><a href="/tools/json-yaml/">JSON ↔ YAML</a></td><td>Creating config files from JSON data</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Decode JWT payload</td><td><a href="/tools/jwt-decoder/">JWT Decoder</a></td><td>Inspecting auth tokens during debugging</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Compare JSON versions</td><td><a href="/tools/diff-checker/">Diff Checker</a></td><td>Finding what changed in an API response</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
`
